--==================================================
-- LBB DESYNC — GALAXY EDITION
--
-- SNAP & ACT: resumes packets for ONE frame,
-- fires all nearby interactions/remotes, then
-- re-pauses. Server processes interaction at
-- your real position before snapping you back.
--==================================================

